動、學生運動，對門市有啲損失」，但對長和系公司影響「損失好少」，強調「要講良心說話」。"},{"pid":"737a025309f0730c24bc58f97a0e7dd30d5c8bdb","tid":1985430,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:44:23.000Z","msg":"其實支持自由貿易，公平競爭<br />\n公平選舉<br />\n只算係一個正常有良知既人<br />\n其實下下分黃藍<br />\n我估好多自稱黃既連自己都唔清楚定義<br />\n有人想建國，有人想反共，有人想真普選，<br />\n有人亦只想安樂茶飯<br />\n標籤扣帽子只係中共常用手段<br />\n標籤左你係黃係獨係反中反華就好打壓<br />\nFF邊個名人係黃根本意義唔大"},{"pid":"2a221d170fa6d211a16d26f74697a708e91d297b","tid":1985430,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T07:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXuh2c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXuh2c0.jpg&h=534e74c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0bcec34093517c460f85a481810cb33f326dad","tid":1985430,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:05:30.000Z","msg":"和你黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}